ISRAEL; HUSSEIN, SADDAM; CHEMICAL WEAPONS -- IRAQ; ISRAEL -- FOREIGN RELATIONS 
-- SYRIA; ISRAEL -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ARAB NATIONS; NUCLEAR WEAPONS -- 
ISRAEL 
</P>
