DEFICIENCY SYNDROME; BIRTH CONTROL DEVICES; PREVENTIVE MEDICINE; LOS ANGELES 
CITY COUNCIL; POLITICAL ACTIVISM; DEMONSTRATIONS -- LOS ANGELES 
</P>
