BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski, who ended the week with a $60 loss on Sunday, 
will try to get back on the winning track today when his wager is a $12 triple 
from Native Pocket, Risen Port and No Doubles Match in the sixth to 
Somethingdifferent in the seventh to Olympic Prospect in the eighth. Bob, who 
started the meeting with a mythical $1,000 bankroll, is now at $1,020.40. 
</P>
