<P>
Universal, Cosby Sign Pact: Universal Pictures has signed a two-year deal with 
TV sitcom star Bill Cosby, who will produce and star in several movies. The 
pact gives Universal first look at all feature films developed by Cosby, whose 
television series, "The Cosby Show," has been at the top, or near the top, of 
