</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
More Entertainment: The Metropolitan Opera Assn. has selected Entertainment 
Corp. U.S.A. as the exclusive presenter of summer attractions at the 
Metropolitan Opera House from 1991-1994. The agreement marks the first time 
since the Sol Hurok era that an outside presenter has entered into a long-term 
