<P>
ORANGE COUNTY GRAND JURY; WOMEN -- HEALTH; MEDICAL CARE -- ORANGE COUNTY; 
HOSPITALS -- ORANGE COUNTY; POLLS; PREGNANCY; INDIGENTS; MEDI CAL; DOCTORS; 
